CMD: shadow-56vm6.shadow.whamcloud.com mount -t lustre -o user_xattr,flock shadow-56vm3@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre
mount.lustre: mount shadow-56vm3@tcp:/lustre at /mnt/lustre failed: Input/output error
Is the MGS running?
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Looks similar to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7193&quot; title=&quot;sanity-scrub: No sub tests failed in this test set&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7193&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7193&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

